title: Looking for player to join team! (bronze/silver, teen)
body:
Hey, we are a team of 4 players that need a 5th!

We are looking for someone high bronze/low silver who's 14-16 years old. Must be willing to Skype.

We are looking for a jungler or ADC.

Add me on League if interested, and thanks for reading!
